/p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section style=\"background-color:#F6F5F2;padding:80px 56px;border-bottom:1px solid #DDDDDD\"><div style=\"max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;gap:64px\"><div><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#00897B;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:12px\">03</p><h2 style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#111111;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:16px\">Organisational Design &amp; Studio Builds</h2><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#888888;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px\">Building the production capability organisations need — from the ground up.</p><div style=\"padding:16px 20px;background-color:#E8F5F3;border-radius:4px\"><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#00695C;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px\">For</p><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#00695C;line-height:1.5\">Brands insourcing production. Agencies building or fixing production departments.</p></div></div><div><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#555555;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:32px\">Whether you are insourcing for the first time, restructuring an underperforming department, or building a new studio from scratch, we design the structure, define the roles, and support the build.</p><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #DDDDDD;padding-top:24px\"><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#888888;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px\">What this includes</p><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px 32px\"><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start\"><span style=\"color:#00897B;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px\">›</span><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555555;line-height:1.5\">In-house production department design</p></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start\"><span style=\"color:#00897B;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px\">›</span><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555555;line-height: